Xambit is a library that standardizes the sending and receiving of data across
a FIFO object. It also mandates a user defined validation hook that determines
whether or not the data is allowed to be divluged or ingested. 

Building and installation
=========================
On STOP: 
-------
autoreconf -i
./configure --prefix=/xts --libdir=/xts/lib64
make
make install


On Linux: 
--------
autoreconf -i
./configure
make
make install
